com.burstly.lib.component.networkcomponent.burstly
Class AudioControlReciever

java.lang.Object
  android.content.BroadcastReceiver
      com.burstly.lib.component.networkcomponent.burstly.AudioControlReciever

public class AudioControlReciever
extends BroadcastReceiver

Class is used to control volume level for video. It is used as a BroadcastReceiver to recieve notifications about changing ringer mode.

Author:
Alexey Redinskii
